dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Billy Morgan. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Margaret Brown.
Great to meet you, Margaret. Can you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six two eight nine.
Thank you, Margaret. Can you also confirm the make and model of your vehicle for our records?
It's a two zero one seven Toyota Camry.
Thank you for that information, Margaret. We will update our records accordingly. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all. Thank you, Billy, for your help.
You're welcome, Margaret. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Goodbye.
